<DOCNO> LA112290-0015 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 311512 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 22, 1990, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
North County Focus; Page 12; Metro Desk 
