<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: BABY WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BETH KLEID , Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Life Goes On: Patti LuPone gave birth Wednesday to a baby boy, Joshua Luke 
Johnston. 
</P>
<P>
The child was born to the actress and her husband, cameraman Matt Johnston, at 
Cedars Sinai Hospital. But Lupone's character on the ABC series "Life Goes On," 
Libby Thacher, continues her pregnancy. Her baby will not arrive until the end 
of the television season. LuPone won a Tony for her performance on Broadway in 
"Evita." BETH KLEID 
</P>
</TEXT>
