<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO SPOTLIGHT: STAGE / NANCY CHURNIN: DIRECTOR O'BRIEN STEPS OUT ON 
CENTER STAGE FOR 'LETTERS' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By NANCY CHURNIN 
