<TEXT>
<P>
PROGRAM NOTES: Sledgehammer Theatre will have three Pay What You Can 
performances of "Leonce and Lena" Nov. 29 at 8 p.m., Dec. 2 at 2 p.m. and Dec. 
12 at 8 p.m. . . . 
</P>
