By DONNA DOWLING 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In a dramatic shift, the Port Hueneme City Council moved veteran Councilman 
Orvene Carpenter into the mayor's job Wednesday night, ousting Dorill B. 
Wright, mayor for nearly 17 years. 
</P>
