<HEADLINE>
<P>
PRO FOOTBALL REPORT / WEEKDAY UPDATE; 
</P>
<P>
RAMS; 
</P>
<P>
ELLARD MAY NOT PLAY AGAINST 49ERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By TIM KAWAKAMI 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ram receiver Henry Ellard was listed as questionable with a sore right 
hamstring Wednesday, and Coach John Robinson suggested that Ellard isn't 
expected to play against San Francisco Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
If Ellard can't play, Robinson said that rookie receiver Tony Lomack, who has 
been on the injured-reserve list all season, will probably be activated. TIM 
KAWAKAMI 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112290-0193 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 311954 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
