Photo, COLOR, Jim Everett is concentrating on Sunday's game against the 49ers; 
he won't be sidetracked by the media. GAIL FISHER / Los Angeles Times; Table, 
(Orange County Edition) EVERETT'S NUMBERS 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
