CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SAUDI ARABIA; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SAUDI ARABIA; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI 
ARABIA 
</P>
