now playing volleyball at Stanford, is following in her sisters' footsteps. ; 
Photo, Bev Oden, who led Irvine to two state titles and was an All-American as 
a freshman at Stanford, is playing better than ever this season. ROD SEARCEY / 
For The Times; Photo, Bev Oden 
</P>
